In other sectors of the processing industry, rising prices evolved between 0.6 percent and 9.1 percent. 
In the whole of the processing industry, prices have increased by 10.2 percent over the past year. 
The price of supply of electricity, gas, steam and water have exceeded by 18.7 percent the previous year. 
Among the groups of internal trade and the allocation of sectors, in August, are the initiators of profit on investment showed a rise in the most significant monthly price (0.7 percent). 
