In the sectors of production of consumer goods, inflation measured 6.8 percent, while the initiators of profit, a reduction of 1.4 percent. 
The sale price in the export of the industrial sector, HUF, have increased by 1.1 percent in August from the previous month, while they have suffered a decline of 3.9 percent over 12 months. 
